{"tid":1501740,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中央如何拆解？ 王振民：幕後黑手將負沉重代價","createTime":"2019-08-24T12:40:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T08:39:56.000Z","uid":68738,"like":52,"dislike":68,"uniUserReply":108,"replies":[{"pid":"c5da1af56149dcffdf047ee27d9ad2ff28bded36","tid":1501740,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:40:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190824/large/1566636293_c46f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190824%2Flarge%2F1566636293_c46f.jpg&h=eb9e5fed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港反送中抗爭持續至今，中央一直沒有正面回應事件，亦沒透露如何處理、解決香港的困局。中聯辦法律部前部長、清華大學港澳研究中心主任王振民今日（24日）在深圳出席一個座談會時，認為目前香港「得了大病和重病」，但認為中央「不會拋棄或離棄香港」，並稱想看到香港、內地「自相殘殺」的人是做夢，對事件背後的黑手和毒害青年的人，他認為要負上沉重的代價。<br />\n<br />\n王振民認為，近日反送中抗爭，「一國兩制」中的「一國」被瘋狂和肆意破壞，他認為，如果街頭暴力不停止，「中央是否會繼續允許香港實施一國兩制」。他重申，要繼續實施「一國兩制」的前提，是要「滿足『一國』的基本要求」。<br />\n<br />\n中央至今未有表態如何應對香港的情況，王振民認為相信中央「不會感情用事」、「不會拋棄或離棄香港」，並會「與香港同胞站在一起、不離不棄、共渡難關」。雖然中央「對香港有信心，對香港年輕人有耐心」，但他認為中央「絕對不會放過事件背後的黑手和毒害青年的人」，將要「他們負上沉重代價」，他更認為，想看到內地和香港「自相殘殺的人」是「做夢」。<br />\n<br />\n出席同一個座談會的港澳辦前副主任、全國港澳研究會會長徐澤則認為，目前香港正面臨「嚴峻考驗」，形容正發生「有遺害的事情」，「長時間持續，會令香港有沉淪的危險」，他更指目前是「守護或毀掉一國兩制之戰」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190824&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=59969241\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190824%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D59969241&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOgqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=2f1b6b74\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190824%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D59969241&h=57a21b87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190824&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=59969241</a>"},{"pid":"58dfa76ea99fc0a37f20d8e9299da84fa7b5a0b9","tid":1501740,"uid":8441,"like":76,"dislike":0,"score":76,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:41:26.000Z","msg":"當年推行通識科既高官<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3b35086f68d7e72bc72273dab287cfe88651864","tid":1501740,"uid":392,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:41:52.000Z","msg":"陸頌雄？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f838cf30cafe8cd59382802ce1c400ccf6725d6b","tid":1501740,"uid":93986,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:42:06.000Z","msg":"林鄭玩完"},{"pid":"3e695827e656bfbfd929995ccb1ce6b0d5a5d2d4","tid":1501740,"uid":118120,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:43:02.000Z","msg":"香港班狗官就係一切既幕後黑手<br />\n係佢地將香港出賣先會搞到今日局面<br />\n每一個高官都有罪＿"},{"pid":"9390fabaaef392c4e51a08cc083c6b0268ab6a3b","tid":1501740,"uid":2924,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:43:04.000Z","msg":"林鄭今次仆街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31772033c7968c915607d621d93f9d99e215a30a","tid":1501740,"uid":304321,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:43:52.000Z","msg":"幕後黑手: 林太！"},{"pid":"eb88c03c140cf73af81a74ab3c71e9fa75f26042","tid":1501740,"uid":229835,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:44:16.000Z","msg":"拋棄啦"},{"pid":"1ea13f80228c62439bc8a697d264405448cb8942","tid":1501740,"uid":59854,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:44:32.000Z","msg":"老懵懂rip"},{"pid":"77fe7d7ba5dca98c0e23f5953c8e90a684aca014","tid":1501740,"uid":262674,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:44:37.000Z","msg":"梁振英同林奠"},{"pid":"753bf7df82a59db27be82939e6e548c3eaf78f89","tid":1501740,"uid":180171,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:44:47.000Z","msg":"硬係要自己ff個大台出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0c0bda1a38d4e5e391c2e687253aeebd3e661e5","tid":1501740,"uid":104507,"like":12,"